<h2 id="section-top">Speech and language services</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=2699">Oxleas NHS Foundation Trust</a>
</p>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="service-locations clear">
<div class="panel edit-box">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p class="address">Children's Development Centre, 3rd Floor, B Block<br/>01322 521330</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent5e195b48a3af41de99841d4226de9c06">
</div>
<div id="stcpDiv">
<p>Our small team of specialist speech and language therapists and therapy assistants provide assessment, diagnosis and therapy for children's speech, language and communication needs and provide specialist support for children with feeding and swallowing difficulties.</p>
<p>We run clinics at the Children’s Development Centre here at Queen Mary’s Hospital, as well as community clinics. We also see children and young people in their own home, school or nursery.</p>
</div></div>
</div>
</div>
